\title{Teaching grant successful}
\date{2026-05-15}
\author{liamoc}
\p{I'm happy to report that the small grant I applied for with [[cpmpercussion]] was successful. We will get a few thousand dollars to set up a teaching activity where students will program with \em{punch cards} again. }
\p{The key to this approach will be having only \em{one} card reading/program executing machine for all students, who must then book computer time just like in the old days of batch processing. I also thing there's something important about the physicality of punching holes in cards that students might appreciate. It's also LLM-proof programming, so there's that.}
